 Roles and Responsibilities
 Develop AI and machine learning solutions to optimise business performance across different areas of the organisation;
 Use data analytics to help in-country Marketing, Distribution and Operation teams to increase revenue, lower costs and improve operational efficiency;
 Identify actionable insights from analytics solutions, and communicate this to relevant stakeholders to improve decision making and drive business performance;
 Develop in depth understanding of the business and be able to advise the business on the right analytics approach by participating in business discussions and presentations as applicable;
